üîç Properties Used in This Example:----

| Property / Feature  | Description                              |
| ------------------- | ---------------------------------------- |
| `modifier`          | Controls size, padding, clickable, etc.  |
| `clickable`         | Adds click listener with ripple feedback |
| `interactionSource` | Tracks state (like pressed)              |
| `shape`             | Rounded corners                          |
| `elevation`         | Controls shadow                          |
| `colors`            | Sets container and content color         |
| `border`            | Adds border around the card              |
| `Image`             | Shows a profile or content image         |
| `Text`              | Displays name and role                   |
| `IconButton`        | Adds an actionable icon (with listener)  |


üì¶ Required Dependencies:---
Make sure these are added in your build.gradle:
    implementation("androidx.compose.material3:material3:1.2.0")
    implementation("androidx.compose.ui:ui:1.5.0")

